    public class TSimpleObservableList<E>
extends javafx.beans.property.SimpleListProperty<E>
implements ITObservableList<E>
     This implementation of ITObservableList have methods which indicates when the list or your itens are changed.
 
 Important:
 Use the TFXCollections iTObservableList() method to get a proxy instance of this Class, 
 the proxy returned will calculate the property t_hashCodeProperty every time the list or a item is changed.
    Author:
    Davis Gordon
    See Also:
    SimpleListProperty
